data.description: Beautiful 4 bed 2 1/2 bath home on 11.25 acres! Property features a 36X48 shop with its own 200 Amp service. Carport and a two stall barn. Covered area for your RV or horse trailer. New metal roof 2016. Views of Mt St. Helens, Adams, Rainier, Hood and the 3 sisters on a clear day! Don't miss out on this one! Call your realtor and make your appointment today!
